701121f.title: Bronx: Goulden Avenue - Bedford Park Boulevard
701121f.text:
Goulden Ave. (running from right to left in center of view) between
Bedford Park Boulevard and West 195th Street, showing the thoroughfare
under construction. This area was formerly part of the Jerome Park
Reservoir. The view is in a westerly direction.
April 27, 1936.
Works Progress Administration.
Federal Art Project photo.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
